= TZInfo Data

TZInfo Data contains the tz database (http://www.twinsun.com/tz/tz-link.htm)
packaged as a set of Ruby modules. The tz database is used to create the 
zoneinfo directory on many Unix and Unix-like machines.

TZInfo Data is intended to be used with TZInfo[http://tzinfo.rubyforge.org].


== Installation

The preferred method of installing TZInfo Data is using RubyGems[http://docs.rubygems.org/]:

  % gem install tzinfo-data


== Download

Gem, tar.gz and zip packages for TZInfo Data can be found at 

* http://rubyforge.org/frs/?group_id=894


